@NODE PROBS "DO YOU HAVE ANY PROBLEMS?"


			MAIN-PROBLEMS AND THEIR SOLUTION:
			=================================

- THE OUTPUT OF CALLER-SPY IS FULL OF RUBBISH, SEEMS TO BE TOTALLY CONFUSED

->Just delete the two files `astoday.cfg` and `asyester.cfg` located in the
  Dir `DOORS:Caller-Spy/`! After that start Caller-Spy ONCE with the number
  of Users set to an value, that guarantees that all users from TODAY AND
  YESTERDAY are shown.

  (if you`re not sure how to change the user`s-shown-value check the
   description of the @{"CONFiGFiLE" LiNK CONFiGFiLES} in this doc-file!)

  If that didn`t correct the problem, have a look into your callerslog and
  check if it look`s normal! If it doesn`t look normal, just delete it or
  change the corrupt data inside manually! Then start Caller-Spy again with
  the above mentioned settings!

  If all that didn`t solve your problem, just contact me on the BBS` below!
  Else set the value of users shown back to the normal value and be happy!



